_header: There was one Philip king some tide
_description: ‘De decollacione sancti Iohannis baptiste’, in the ‘expanded’ Northern Homily Cycle

BLHar4196.First Lines: Þare was ane Philyp king sum tydeof yturie and of trachomde…
BLHar4196.Last Lines: …God len us so to leue all sinÞat we vntill his welth may win
